{"tid":1969730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屌你班連登仔幾時先學識擺脫風向L同五毛？幾時先有獨立思考同國際視野（多圖）","createTime":"2020-04-12T15:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T23:38:41.000Z","uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc681abcc9ed5ef218b188bc8f764e31b1ec948","tid":1969730,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以下內容轉載自Hello UK goodbye HK，今次佢講得太正確，今次我撐佢</span></strong><br />\n其實真係好攰好心淡，幾十年嘅國際組織，英國話恆常繼續比錢，呢個係合約精神，而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留條Content Farm嘅「新聞」</span></strong>，留响唔關事嘅Post即係點？我從來分享國新聞都唔會剩係一個媒體，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要Cross check同fact check</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n再者，你估係藍店呀，話唔幫襯就唔幫襯咁呀，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國際事務好似屋企咁運作，到底幾時有些少國際視野？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n然後，邊個國家嘅國會推動G20衛生組織取代WHO，係英國！<br />\n<br />\n再退一萬步，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人好痛苦？知唔知英國因為武漢肺炎死咗幾多人？幾多人要被家居坐監軟禁？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以前講咗好多次，呢個Page最憎怨婦，自製國際敵人，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">滴水穿石感染國際嘅堅毅到底幾時先識？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nBTW，本人好有記性，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上次講外交委員會出信比G20嘅時候，又係呢位人兄話中國係G20龍頭</span></strong>，視野呀，比啲掙扎啦！<br />\n<br />\n#香港是地球核心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKNB93o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKNB93o.jpg&h=41939488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLUg93p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLUg93p.jpg&h=a7bf3dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=791871488007990&amp;id=153006095227869?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D791871488007990%26id%3D153006095227869%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962ZojwOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=a6ffc2fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=791871488007990&amp;id=153006095227869?sfnsn=mo</a>"},{"pid":"bff09622770f40db7ac2b3e01804ced280fa84d1","tid":1969730,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:23:26.000Z","msg":"乜柒都話連登仔，fb既野又關連登撚事"},{"pid":"1510341c23db73067ca37504718b400fb983ba5e","tid":1969730,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bff09622770f40db7ac2b3e01804ced280fa84d1","tid":1969730,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:23:26.000Z","msg":"乜柒都話連登仔，fb既野又關連登撚事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T16:29:40.000Z","msg":"英國宣布捐2億英鎊給WHO<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1969102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1969102</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9c1ce7731d4637df9c171c131d6b1b953161c846","tid":1969730,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T23:04:46.000Z","msg":"好多消息只要用小小心機諗一諗，就會發覺係共狗請嘅五毛分化狗！<br />\n共狗成日玩分化就係因為個個都懶，個個都佛系要民主！"},{"pid":"e8e7677e29f52764333a8481ef27b3f4dcf40282","tid":1969730,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c1ce7731d4637df9c171c131d6b1b953161c846","tid":1969730,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T23:04:46.000Z","msg":"好多消息只要用小小心機諗一諗，就會發覺係共狗請嘅五毛分化狗！<br />\n共狗成日玩分化就係因為個個都懶，個個都佛系要民主！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:18:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正解"},{"pid":"52d0ba1ded65eac82deb63cc3a3400fe29f2abc6","tid":1969730,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T23:38:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}